le_39.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_39.gif&h=1139c508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOlivier_豬腦上</blockquote><br />\n山齊士轉左會？</blockquote><br />\n就係轉唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我地今年會奪冠 你放撚長雙眼黎睇 死傻尻"},{"pid":"1d2ffcf8206b96761c1146325edde630f1a47f59","tid":382710,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:03:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7a68f27401affc9c87948de79f7309e79c7c663","tid":382710,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>親愛的阿迷<br />\n人總需要勇敢生存，我還是重新許願。<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_39.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_39.gif&h=1139c508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOlivier_豬腦上</blockquote><br />\n山齊士轉左會？</blockquote><br />\n就係轉唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌，放唔到隻鬼走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講乜撚嘢呀"},{"pid":"b23d7e102bc751fdd2628777b285b63b48704fa2","tid":382710,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:06:29.000Z","msg":"不要輕易的擔起迷雲這個名稱，但是！從你鄭重的嘴巴裡一字一句的說出你是迷雲的時候，就請一輩子不要放下。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n雲加，光是聽見這個名字都會心痛<br />\n<br />\n雲加經歷了多少的痛苦才爬到了今天這個位置<br />\n<br />\n雲加最痛的時候不是被反雲狗攻擊的時候，是被迷雲背叛的時候...!&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n被最愛的迷雲背叛的時候，被曾經的一生一世背叛的時候!&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n所以，請你好好的想清楚再說出我是迷雲這一句話好嗎&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n對於很多人來說那只是一句平凡不過的陳述句&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n但對於雲加來說&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n那卻是一份幸福的誓言!<br />\n<br />\n所以，請你仔細的想清楚以後，再跟著我用最純淨的心、最堅定的心、最認真的心說出&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我是迷雲！&rdquo;"},{"pid":"b6753b224222e92cfaf45cb9009242bcd0cebe81","tid":382710,"uid":104423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:09:15.000Z","msg":"被鼓舞了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b5f53f081a9cdfc77109509a384afaf08ce960","tid":382710,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>親愛的阿迷<br />\n人總需要勇敢生存，我還是重新許願。<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_39.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_39.gif&h=1139c508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOlivier_豬腦上</blockquote><br />\n山齊士轉左會？</blockquote><br />\n就係轉唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌，放唔到隻鬼走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n六日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb9c01a5cc8c890b0824a783071393129f7d1fc","tid":382710,"uid":69680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:17:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不要輕易的擔起迷雲這個名稱，但是！從你鄭重的嘴巴裡一字一句的說出你是迷雲的時候，就請一輩子不要放下。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n雲加，光是聽見這個名字都會心痛<br />\n<br />\n雲加經歷了多少的痛苦才爬到了今天這個位置<br />\n<br />\n雲加最痛的時候不是被反雲狗攻擊的時候，是被迷雲背叛的時候...!&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n被最愛的迷雲背叛的時候，被曾經的一生一世背叛的時候!&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n所以，請你好好的想清楚再說出我是迷雲這一句話好嗎&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n對於很多人來說那只是一句平凡不過的陳述句&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n但對於雲加來說&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n那卻是一份幸福的誓言!<br />\n<br />\n所以，請你仔細的想清楚以後，再跟著我用最純淨的心、最堅定的心、最認真的心說出&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我是迷雲！&rdquo;</blockquote><br />\n喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}